{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it's from this time on, it was not gassing, but it doesn't mean transport didn't came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The transport stopped too, but here and there, they brought some people, you know, 30, 40 people, which they killed or-- or-- or you know, they let some of them in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the-- the-- the mass killing was over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Who were the last people to be--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian transport.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian transport.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Personally, I can't point at any of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The last mass [INAUDIBLE] killings was in October 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the killing went on, and the burning we still saw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not such-- in such masses like they did before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we-- you know, then-- I was already the third-- it was already the third winter what I spent in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was also a very, very cold winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here and there, you know, from transports, when we sorted the clothing, we found pieces of newspaper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we saw the war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Besides this, you know, Auschwitz was bombarded too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we who were already better fed and could [? think-- ?] I thought [? of ?] how is it possible that those-- you know, we saw lots of-- of air, you know, planes going over our heads towards Russia-- toward Germany already, not Russia.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Towards Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Russians were already very advanced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they didn't bomb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they bombed quite a few times, but never the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were praying for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At least some of us have a chance to escape, to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But from the escapees, I have to mention it too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was only once very, very successful-- three escapees from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were good friends of ours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We know them very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
